<article id="post-1361" class="post-1361 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-general tag-failure tag-management">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/06/failure-is-an-option/" rel="bookmark">Failure is an option</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>One afternoon, a few years ago now, the head of my department uttered something completely heretical while we were in a fairly high-stressed meeting about some technical difficulties we were having on a project. It was one of those utterances that made everyone take pause, look at him, and wonder if he was off his rocker.<br />
He wasn&#8217;t, for the record. In fact, he was striving for us to not view impending doom as a bad thing. While his two words were at first shocking (especially to the Account Managers present, who&#8217;d ultimately have to deal with the client), it was also one of those moments you sat back and actually thought about what you were doing.<br />
So what did he say?</p>
<blockquote><p>Embrace failure.<br />
<cite>&#8211; Allard Losier</cite></p></blockquote>
<p> <a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/06/failure-is-an-option/#more-1361" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;Failure is an option&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/06/failure-is-an-option/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2009-06-07T13:09:45-06:00">7 June 2009</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/failure/" rel="tag">failure</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/management/" rel="tag">management</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/06/failure-is-an-option/#comments">6 Comments<span class="screen-reader-text"> on Failure is an option</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
